<div style="font-family:'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; max-width: 550px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px; background-color: #0A0A0B; color: #F0F0F5; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #1A1A1E; box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <div style="display: inline-block; width: 48px; height: 48px; background: #7B61FF; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 48px; font-size: 24px;">⚖️</div>
    <h1 style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Action Required</h1>
    <p style="color: #8888A0; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 500;">Obsidian Management Queue</p>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #111114; border: 1px solid #1F1F24; border-radius: 14px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <p style="color: #F0F0F5; font-size: 15px; margin: 0 0 16px; font-weight: 500;">Hello Manager,</p>
    <p style="color: #8888A0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 24px;">A new leave request has been submitted by a team member. Your decision is required to update the organizational schedule:</p>
    
    <div style="background: #0A0A0B; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #7B61FF; margin-bottom: 24px;">
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="color: #5D5D6D; padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px;">Team Member</td>
          <td style="color: #FFFFFF; padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-align: right;">{{employeeName}}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="color: #5D5D6D; padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px;">Classification</td>
          <td style="color: #FFFFFF; padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-align: right; text-transform: capitalize;">{{type}} Leave</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="color: #5D5D6D; padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px;">Duration</td>
          <td style="color: #FFFFFF; padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-align: right;">{{startDate}} &rarr; {{endDate}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #1A1A1E; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 20px;">
      <p style="color: #5D5D6D; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 0 0 8px; font-weight: 700;">Employee's Reason</p>
      <p style="color: #D1D1D1; font-size: 13px; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">"{{reason}}"</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 32px; text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/admin/leaves" style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 32px; background: #7B61FF; color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px;">Review in Admin Panel →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center;">
    <p style="color: #44444D; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
      As a manager, you are responsible for maintaining team coverage during leave periods.
    </p>
    <div style="margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid #1A1A1E;">
      <p style="color: #333338; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">&copy; 2026 Obsidian Enterprise Leave Management System</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
